onChange.script:
import traceback
	
	try:
		dataset = currentValue.value
		system.perspective.print(dataset)
		if dataset == None:
			#system.perspective.sendMessage("newParticipantsReferralsMonthly", payload = {"newParticipantsReferralsMonthly": 0}, scope = "page")
			return
		
		#Get selected participants
		idlist = []
		uniqueCount = 0
		hmisCount = 0
		numRows = dataset.getRowCount()
	
		participantIdsData = system.dataset.filterColumns(dataset, ["participantId"]) ## get one column from adtaset
		participantIdsData = system.dataset.toPyDataSet(participantIdsData) ## convert to pydatset for easy iteration
		participantIdsList = [row[0] for row in participantIdsData] ## convert to list
		participantIdsSet = set(participantIdsList) ## Set will remove the duplicate participant Ids
		uniqueList = list(participantIdsSet)
		uniqueCount = len(participantIdsSet)
		
		system.perspective.print("numRows : " + str(numRows))
		system.perspective.print("uniqueCount : " + str(uniqueCount))
		
		hmisData = system.dataset.filterColumns(dataset, ["HMIS"]) ## get HMIS columns
		hmisData = system.dataset.toPyDataSet(hmisData) ## convert to pyds for easy iteratiin
		hmisList = [row[0] for row in hmisData] ## convert to list
		hmisCount = hmisList.count(True) ## count HMIS with value True
		
		system.perspective.print("hmisCount : " + str(hmisCount))
		
		if (numRows > 0):
			pctHMIS = 100 * hmisCount / numRows
		else:
			pctHMIS = 0
		
		system.perspective.print("pctHMIS : " + str(pctHMIS))
		system.perspective.print(str(uniqueList))
		
#		strIdList = ','.join(uniqueList) ## convert to comma separated string
		strIdList = str(uniqueList).replace('[','').replace(']','')
		system.perspective.print("strIdList : " + str(strIdList))
		params = {"IdList": strIdList}

		#KPI3 Interviews Monthly
		result3 = system.db.runNamedQuery("Participants/Services/KPI/ServicesMonthly", params)
		MonthCount = 6
		servicesMonthly = []
		now = system.date.now()
		for i in reversed(range(MonthCount)):
			imonthago = system.date.addMonths(now, -i)
			cmonthago = system.date.addMonths(imonthago, 1)
			month = system.date.getMonth(imonthago) + 1
			dateMonth = system.date.getMonth(imonthago)
			dateYear = system.date.getYear(imonthago)
			date = system.date.getDate(dateYear, dateMonth, 01)
			datetime = system.date.setTime(date, 00, 00, 00)
			append_item = {"time": system.date.format(datetime, "M/d/yyyy") , "Participants": 0}
			resultMonths = 0
			for row in range(result3.getRowCount()):
				resultMonth = result3.getValueAt(row, "service_month")
				if month == resultMonth:
					resultMonths += 1
					
			append_item["Participants"] = resultMonths
			servicesMonthly.append(append_item)

			#Update Applicants Per Month KPIs
			system.perspective.sendMessage("servicesMonthly", payload = {"servicesMonthly": servicesMonthly, "serviceCount": numRows, "uniqueCount": uniqueCount, "pctHMIS": pctHMIS}, scope = "page")
				
	except:
		logger = system.util.getLogger("Participants Referral Dashboard Table custom.SQLData KPI")
		msg = traceback.format_exc()
		logger.error(msg)

### Refresh data
	#system.perspective.print("Refresh Services Dashboard")
	self.refreshBinding("props.data")
	self.props.selection.selectedRow = None

import traceback
	try:
		#Send the dataset to Excel
		self.props.style.cursor = "wait"
		filename = 'Participants_Services_' + str(system.date.format(system.date.now(),"yyyyMMddHHmmss")) + '.xls'
		dataset = self.props.data
		display_columns = ["name", "nickName","genderName","serviceDate","HMIS","employeeName","quantity","programName","serviceName","serviceLocation","comment"]
		NewDataset = system.dataset.filterColumns(dataset, display_columns)
		xlFile = system.dataset.toExcel(True,NewDataset)
		system.perspective.download(filename, xlFile)
		self.props.style.cursor = None
		
	except:   
		logger = system.util.getLogger("Participants Services tableToExcel")
		msg = traceback.format_exc()
		logger.error(msg)
